h2. AWS Services Inventory (18 Services)

h3. Networking

|| Service || Details ||
| *VPC* | 2 public subnets, Internet Gateway |
| *Security Group* | Controls ECS Fargate inbound/outbound |

h3. Auth & Identity

|| Service || Details ||
| *Cognito User Pool* | {{prompt2test-users}} — login, passwords, sessions |
| *Cognito Groups* | Each team = one group; resolved from {{cognito:groups}} JWT claim |
| *Identity Pool* | Maps users to IAM roles for SDK calls |
| *Cognito Auth Role (IAM)* | Permissions the React UI gets after login |

h3. Data Layer

|| Service || Details ||
| *Aurora Serverless v2* | {{prompt2test-vectors}} — PostgreSQL 16 + pgvector, auto-pauses when idle |
| *RDS Data API* | Lambda calls Aurora without a VPC connection |
| *Secrets Manager* | {{prompt2test/aurora/credentials}} — Aurora password |

h3. Backend Logic

|| Service || Details ||
| *p2t-testcase-writer* | Lambda — saves, updates, deletes test cases & run records, promote action |
| *p2t-testcase-reader* | Lambda — lists, fetches, semantic search via pgvector |
| *CDK Custom Resource Lambda* | One-time DB schema init on first deploy |

h3. AI & Machine Learning

|| Service || Details ||
| *Claude Sonnet 4.5* | Powers the AI agent (test case generation) |
| *Titan Embed Text v2* | Generates vector embeddings for semantic search |
| *AgentCore* | {{Prompt2TestAgent}} — runs agent container on demand, status: READY |

h3. Browser Automation

|| Service || Details ||
| *ECS Fargate Cluster* | {{prompt2test-playwright-cluster}} — on-demand per test run, ARM64 2vCPU/4GB |
| *ECS Task Definition* | Pulls latest image from ECR on each run |
| *ECR* (playwright) | {{prompt2test-playwright-mcp}} — Playwright + noVNC Docker image |
| *ECR* (agent) | {{prompt2test-agent}} — AI agent Docker image |

h3. UI Hosting

|| Service || Details ||
| *Amplify Hosting* | {{Prompt2TestUI}} — serves React app via CloudFront CDN |
| *Auto-deploy* | Push to {{master}} -> Amplify rebuilds automatically |

h3. CI/CD

|| Service || Details ||
| *CodePipeline* (x3) | Lambda, Agent, Playwright MCP pipelines |
| *CodeBuild* | Builds Docker images and Lambda packages |
| *S3 + KMS* | Pipeline artifact storage |

h3. Config & Observability

|| Service || Details ||
| *SSM Parameter Store* | ECS infra config (cluster ARN, task def, subnets, SG) |
| *DynamoDB* | {{prompt2test-config}} — service URLs, test accounts per team/env |
