h2. Users & Frontend

{panel:title=Audience|borderColor=#6366f1|bgColor=#eef2ff}
* *5 teams* (~20 concurrent users)
* Hosted on *Amplify* behind CloudFront CDN
* Auth: *Cognito User Pool* login -> JWT -> Identity Pool -> scoped IAM role
* Team resolved from {{cognito:groups}} claim at login
* 4 environments: dev, qa, uat, prod (switcher in sidebar)
{panel}

----

h2. Agent Backend (Bedrock AgentCore)

|| Property || Value ||
| Agent Runtime ID | {{Prompt2TestAgent-YTVbD4GrTi}} |
| Container | {{prompt2test-agent:latest}} on ECR |
| Runtime | Python + FastAPI on port 8080 |
| LLM | Claude Sonnet 4.5 ({{us.anthropic.claude-sonnet-4-5-20250929-v1:0}}) |
| Framework | AWS Strands SDK |
| Network | PUBLIC mode |

h3. Agent Modes

|| Mode || Description || LLM? || Playwright? ||
| *plan* | Conversational test plan generation | (/) Yes | (x) No |
| *plan_scenario* | Structured steps with \{service.KEY\} templates + config enrichment | (/) Yes | (x) No |
| *start_session* | Spin up ECS Fargate browser task, return noVNC URL | (x) No | (/) Task starts |
| *automate* | Execute plan steps via Playwright MCP, record replay script | (/) Yes | (/) Yes |
| *replay* | Deterministic re-execution of saved replay script | (x) No | (/) Yes |
| *stop_session* | Stop ECS task, cleanup | (x) No | (/) Task stops |

